            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>leek[s] </strong>in half lengthways, wash thoroughly to remove any grit then top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Top, tail, peel and dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-1693827088094-x200.jpg",
