            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the bacon is crisp, add the<strong> sliced onion[s]</strong>, <strong>sliced leek[s] </strong>and<strong> chopped carrot[s] </strong>to the pot with a small pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
