    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have started to soften, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>dried thyme </strong>and <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
