    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained cannellini beans </strong>and <strong>spelt </strong>to the pot with your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and 600ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[780ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cook for 20 min or until the spelt is tender (it will still have a slight bite when cooked) – this is your <strong>bacon, spelt & cannellini bean soup</strong></p>",
